red spectroscopy to probe organic chemistry,\ngas temperatures and kinematics in the planet-forming zones close to a young\nstar.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Nov 2005 09:05:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
